OL,5, The government has insisted all the    
OL,6, correct processes were followed in the 
OL,7, appointment of the BBC's chairman,     
OL,8, Richard Sharp, in early 2021.          
OL,10,FIt follows claims that shortly before  
OL,11,Fbeing given the job, Mr Sharp helped   
OL,12,Fthe then-prime minister, Boris Johnson,
OL,13,Fsecure a loan agreement.               
OL,15,FMr Sharp, Mr Johnson and the government
OL,16,Fall deny there was a conflict of       
OL,17,Finterest.                              
OL,19,FBut Labour has asked the parliamentary 
OL,20,Fstandards watchdog for an inquiry.     
